metadata.name: Blind Velociraptor
metadata.description: One winter, amoung the prehistoric forest, a baby hatched in the nest of a Velociraptor. Despite the frosty breath of the wind, the sun shone very brightly, the snow flickered and also shone... However, he was not destined to see the beauty of the world around him. The little dinosaur was born blind. All his short life will be accompanied only by cold and darkness.
